00:31.200 --> 00:33.426
- [Alex Voiceover]
There are a few seconds

00:34.026 --> 00:36.256
between this life and the next.

00:37.930 --> 00:41.001
Where something
extraordinary can happen.

00:43.591 --> 00:45.265
Where there are no lies.

00:47.664 --> 00:51.174
But in this life
there are so many lies.

00:53.529 --> 00:56.732
The biggest lie we ever buy into

00:57.329 --> 00:59.413
is that we are in control.

01:01.299 --> 01:03.873
I was never in control.

01:04.854 --> 01:06.462
I just thought I was.

01:08.202 --> 01:10.725
Control is an illusion.

01:10.825 --> 01:12.700
- [Claudia] I can't do this anymore.

01:13.000 --> 01:15.236
- [Alex Voiceover] I couldn't stop what happened.

01:16.590 --> 01:18.764
[sobbing]

01:24.805 --> 01:26.120
- [Claudia] We can't
just keep pretending

01:26.220 --> 01:27.808
that this isn't happening!

01:29.327 --> 01:30.987
- [Alex Voiceover] I
was always powerless.

01:31.087 --> 01:33.300
[sobs]

01:33.400 --> 01:34.746
Once I understood that,

01:37.335 --> 01:38.508
there was no way back.

01:40.614 --> 01:43.172
I built my ivory
tower in the sky,

01:43.272 --> 01:45.860
I built it as high as I could.

01:47.897 --> 01:48.897
I had it all.

01:51.314 --> 01:52.315
I was invincible.

01:55.905 --> 01:58.528
But then I was
dragged back down.

02:01.531 --> 02:03.084
We all make the same journey.

02:04.223 --> 02:07.437
There's no ifs, just when.

02:07.537 --> 02:10.889
[suspenseful music]

02:10.989 --> 02:12.473
Straight down.

02:22.138 --> 02:23.622
- [Claudia] You fucking idiot!

02:27.937 --> 02:29.697
I don't know what comes next.

02:46.231 --> 02:47.408
- [Alex Voiceover]
And what do we find

02:47.508 --> 02:49.648
down there in the
depths waiting for us?

02:51.409 --> 02:52.409
Our own demons.

02:54.032 --> 02:55.067
They never went away.

02:57.069 --> 02:58.069
They just sat there.

02:59.486 --> 03:00.486
Patiently.

03:01.211 --> 03:02.799
Knowing we would be back.

03:04.491 --> 03:06.631
- Excuse me, friend.

03:09.599 --> 03:10.738
You can't be down here.

03:20.438 --> 03:21.646
- You know what's coming.

03:24.925 --> 03:26.236
You know what this is.

03:27.341 --> 03:29.930
You know it's all your fault.

03:30.793 --> 03:32.073
- What's my fault?

03:32.173 --> 03:34.179
- She'll never forgive you.

03:34.279 --> 03:36.488
[punching]

03:52.953 --> 03:55.783
[engine rumbling]

04:10.833 --> 04:14.906
- [Alex Voiceover] I
couldn't stop what happened.

